data.description: This is a must see! This spacious 4 sided brick home has much to offer. Features include: rocking chair front porch, cozy family room with a fireplace to snuggle on chilly nights, formal dining room to entertain your most prestige guest. Hardwood floor in formal dining room, like new kitchen with beautiful granite counter top & brand new Jenn-Air stove/oven, all looking over your gorgeous back-yard oasis that has a massive porch that steps down into your inground pool area, fire pit, and lovely serene garden area for when you just need to decompress. Master on main, with a romantic master bath with a soaking tub  and stand up shower. Bonus room upstairs could be 4th bedroom, man cave or whatever.. Plenty of storage in this lovely home. It also has a detached garage for the man with all his toys or that needs a workshop. Nestled on almost 2 beautiful acres in a small brick community in the sought after Union Grove school district. This home has tons of charm & ready for new homeowners.
